OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain persists across northern
OL,6,Fand northwestern Scotland, easing
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. Cloudy with
OL,8,Fpatchy drizzle at first in Northern
OL,9,FIreland and northern England. Dry
OL,10,Felsewhere with sunny spells and breezy
OL,11,Fconditions. Temperatures near normal
OL,12,Fin the north, very warm southward.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FBreezy in the north with
OL,15,Foccasional rain, heaviest in northwest
OL,16,FScotland. Low cloud and hill fog
OL,17,Fredevelop across southwest Britain and
OL,18,Fwestern areas. Elsewhere, fine and dry
OL,19,Fwith clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
