OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FFurther rain or showers
OL,6,Faffect northern areas, though
OL,7,Fgenerally less heavy. Cloudy in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland and northwest England
OL,9,Fwith patchy drizzle. Elsewhere dry and
OL,10,Fsunny, feeling very warm to hot.
